f858e35","tid":1323671,"uid":126603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T15:12:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/MML-ldgjfeo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMML-ldgjfeo&d=FVRAyOQFEUVrsg2I2pbTeWmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=cae6e46a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/MML-ldgjfeo</a>"},{"pid":"e510895e22a6cb4b50e5462464b059b8407fb5c1","tid":1323671,"uid":241085,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:07:42.000Z","msg":"#1風吹egg &bull; 2mo<br />\n你地有冇試過最愛既人唔係你身邊果個，我同以家女朋友拍拖半年，但每當見到以前女朋友既生活照（無再follow ig但睇佢朋友見到）你都會心痛同掛住以前既時光。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申同前度拍左1年<br />\n同現任都差唔多一年（好中意現任但低落都會想佢）"},{"pid":"e4932ac65e9e0b8fcccabceafc7e23e1e22468ac","tid":1323671,"uid":241085,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:13:39.000Z","msg":"負責任就生 無野係會有心理準備<br />\n套穿左都唔食事後係咩玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n落仔對女仔身體傷害好大<br />\n就算落左補得好<br />\n都唔等於會有機會再陀到下一個<br />\n呢啲係個女仔既考慮啦<br />\n可能無你 佢屋企人都會幫佢養大個b<br />\n而家係你或者你屋企會唔會負責任<br />\n你未有心理準備做人老公做人爸爸<br />\n似係你心理關口多過個女仔未出社會事喎"},{"pid":"377bac87e3f53f61c018309636d8c1960dadf8e6","tid":1323671,"uid":270352,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:22:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e6e47d1f0b6e207a3072753c0128620e437cb1de","tid":1323671,"uid":79485,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:56:11.000Z","msg":"爸爸"},{"pid":"fd404bfe70d3ce5ee3fcd5af85de38127ad77ac6","tid":1323671,"uid":22535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"976965eae5f37cd16a22f29c0cfdc44533b8e100","tid":1323671,"uid":248664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T10:21:48.000Z","msg":"岩岩出左社會工作兩年，今日女朋友同我講有左1個月....完全未ready做一個爸爸，心態同金錢都係未ready 但女朋友就想生左出黎，唔想無左一個生命，但我女朋友仲有兩年大學未讀完，要生就要休學再遲一年先出黎做野<br />\n<br />\n利申：佢父母同意生落黎 ，我父母唔同意，認為我未夠成熟<br />\n兩邊都係私樓 但無乜儲蓄 仲還緊學費 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n應該點做先好，好亂，黎緊年尾好大可能會升職/轉工，以家好似被抗亂曬所有節奏"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:57:38.000Z","msg":"中出得咁過癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3615d035ca53c8e129fc795884319140f18e112f","tid":1323671,"uid":230054,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:17:34.000Z","msg":"25歲差唔多啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd84c9550af4001661691bf546c4916787c8cf47","tid":1323671,"uid":173326,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:32:54.000Z","msg":"你父母緊係唔同意啦，你咁仆街都係佢地生出嚟，佢地都唔會好人得去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個腦唔成熟、下體早熟，你全家食屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"902140ae1ad06db6522205f79c4c48a212891249","tid":1323671,"uid":233593,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T09:42:33.000Z","msg":"做男人有成擔 生出黎擺響外家湊<br />\n預左自己未來兩三年份糧扣除必要開資全數上繳外家養B<br />\n就算唔夠養要外家貼有誠意都唔會怪你<br />\n同外家傾下駛唔駛生B前簽紙結婚先<br />\n再plan兩三年後先住埋都未遲<br />\n喂今舖分分鐘慳左搞結婚壇大龍鳳<br />\n自己屋企果邊唔駛理住，到生左出黎佢地會變樣"},{"pid":"dbe0e5ee20a801031c75c06f338836cd92fa1b16","tid":1323671,"uid":16168,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T11:18:50.000Z","msg":"25歲仲以為自己好細個？<br />\n咩好亂咩plan<br />\n冇錯 落咗你就一身輕<br />\n條女就呢世記得入手術室/食藥 有幾驚有幾痛<br /